<p><me>\textbf{Equality of Complex numbers}</me></p>
<p>
    Two complex numbers <m>z_1 = a + ib</m> and <m>z_2 = c + id</m> are equal iff <m>a = c </m> &amp; <m>b = d </m>.
</p>

<example>
    <statement>
        <p>
            If <m>z_1 = 2 + ix</m> and <m>z_2 = y + 6i</m> are equal, then find the value of <m>x</m> &amp; <m>y</m>.
        </p>
    </statement>
    <solution>
        <p>
            <m>x = 6</m>, <m>y = 2</m>.
        </p>
    </solution>
</example>

